rer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="Anthropic 推出人工智能代理来执行金融服务任务"&gt;处理更广泛的金融服务任务&lt;/a&gt;，表示他们可以为客户会议起草宣传材料、审查财务报表以及升级合规审查案例。这些新工具共有 10 个，直接针对银行、保险、资产管理和金融技术领域的专业人士。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;今年 2 月，Anthropic 的一款自动化工具&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/I3XmTChJzB8aXM1_IXRcoI9_IxzjIezFvt3lNpYIWtwDkfTIbxtIaaHW8NrBCQ_BXcUqaVvM5rTA8Gz2yiBCDDmjiUfW2O3DNUKubSJTf6iTy2MbwwHOPOdcCtsJEf-gNxFDnw03f77HVwkU3j_ZJQVPmKdTy7U4FqeeYZi8VSlOyhbKV-YajLlWQ0VAugLapUtOGcnv2G0vdhNf9ezbpDmYwwpoc4fkHK8-eWZJSgXo15ceSHA-xQbWpCf9GpQGpHonPDrzcAOU3BtVhLCLhweJYk96TmIYuiyAQZ4hAnCOhiM7zSV9SNFjZuEV030Ua1RntWZeE2xE2aOmGTZzBza5P8tIKuTDrbgTZJmn4CWxjUGo45T1ebCWpDVBJs2Ck3f77bDBdvAHKxeThoXCZySFnFfto6hIwDES7yfq3C9r_yK88UUmw3jg9yKNdkMBMusQowJgn2gAHM1iFf0JmUJmAc6fCfaLl4lqc_pFs-faGwFJwEyd1G9gpp5VVkSaqQaQlO9Nn-SO9Ytg2r9a4B2sezxP/3P3T3x6aWndDtHX6RN6pugw5PeNSFtCr/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="人类人工智能工具引发从软件到更广阔市场的抛售"&gt;引发了软件、金融服务和资产管理行业股票价值 2850 亿美元的暴跌，&lt;/a&gt;因为投资者竞相抛售风险敞口很小的股票。周二的反应&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/wnqowqbGUcfmWJtS2YQKzDpGrPnDumYlM0u1PdtI81kSv_7WNaRxXBWqSf1K0p4ex6jFz0UQpQ_LX74F6zLhvLZhAhbtOrBpgYbd6bE04pBHUnXBaIMedcA08d9UqfrlCbsdykCJ9l9FIHlOzk3mukI5OIK9yUz3OW45NzsE8Yt92PQMpD4tEY_l-eBrfBHsVbbcymGhN6Sha5TPGxS2flt_z7PkSqglHzbT5hzl9BbB-LHbS4e2kxJ0OjKB4yKfnuV-PcWkfEp9TB0uIDKj_FCeRI2VPR4RbIsADXt3Bv769P0wnz4qZ5m1uDv8rgaduqGQJZtA92TfKGt4qzypknn4ID-O_V3j-ATBbr7AWby5wf7SaGIkostKq04MIirvSuollwRumSD7LsK0ce0zw8scH6hy3DpaM6C1F9qFb4D6xrYh3e6wPdPZPkgsI1aK9tiIvQfA5wGjOSmFsMruMqf7lvlFZwVzb3BTCpnIAIUiQ4xOL2Yzdblr2U5RJjOdAXV931KkibuD9g7thXE7LA9grYhgXg/fjlvOc49tPGAc6uqKArQ352HC3jznL7G/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着休战的进行，股市上涨至创纪录水平，油价下跌：市场结束"&gt;并没有那么引人注目&lt;/a&gt;，尽管对一些人来说肯定是不愉快的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/CPXX